WEBVTT

00:01.354 --> 00:03.056
Max, I can't wait to go home

00:03.057 --> 00:05.537
and ilegally download that documentary
about performance art.

00:05.554 --> 00:07.034
And I can't wait to go home and watch

00:07.035 --> 00:08.237
"Here comes Honey Boo Boo."

00:08.954 --> 00:10.237
But first you have to see this.

00:10.354 --> 00:12.037
Her name is Marina Abramovic.

00:12.038 --> 00:14.918
In the 90's she and her boyfriend
did this piece called "Confrontation"

00:14.919 --> 00:17.039
where they just slapped
each other's faces for days.

00:17.338 --> 00:18.003
Yeah?

00:18.004 --> 00:19.537
My mom and her boyfriend did that too,

00:19.539 --> 00:22.390
but they called it,
"Who smoked the last cigarette."

00:22.392 --> 00:25.042
No, really, it was pure art.
She's a genius.

00:25.044 --> 00:28.212
How about you and I
do a little art right now?

