What are they doing?

00:41.019 --> 00:42.485
I think they might be doing a scene

00:42.487 --> 00:44.554
from <i>Fifty Shades Of Grey.</i>

00:49.160 --> 00:50.827
Okay, stop.

00:50.829 --> 00:52.162
Okay.

00:55.767 --> 00:57.687
That's for suggesting
we make a lip-synch video

00:57.688 --> 00:59.936
to <i>Call Me Maybe.</i>

