16:22.548 --> 16:25.216
Hi, honey.

16:25.218 --> 16:27.118
Hello?

16:27.120 --> 16:28.986
Honey, I forgot my ticket.

16:28.988 --> 16:30.287
He has my ticket.

16:30.289 --> 16:32.156
Han, this nice usher man thinks I snuck

16:32.158 --> 16:34.725
into the theater,
so just show him the tickets.

16:38.297 --> 16:39.630
You two are together?

16:40.132 --> 16:42.333
- Yeah, why?
- It's nothing.

16:42.335 --> 16:43.567
