16:53.346 --> 16:56.180
I thought I put the ticket in here.

16:56.182 --> 16:58.682
Tickets. You put two tickets
in there, honey.

16:59.184 --> 17:02.119
Okay.

17:02.121 --> 17:05.589
I cannot find it.
Damn.

17:05.590 --> 17:08.092
Sir, you know
that sneaking into a theater's

17:08.094 --> 17:09.160
