17:09.162 --> 17:10.695
It is?

17:13.832 --> 17:15.598
Han, what's that face?

17:15.601 --> 17:18.303
It's the same face I made when I peed...

17:19.305 --> 17:21.672
Honey.

17:21.674 --> 17:24.308
How will I live with the shame?

17:24.310 --> 17:25.976
Well, at least your fanny pack

17:25.978 --> 17:28.712
