thing about you any more.

17:35.887 --> 17:39.190
Well, well, well, look who it is.

17:39.692 --> 17:41.693
Hair flip and go.

17:42.695 --> 17:45.129
I don't know what you're
doing, but it feels weird.

17:45.131 --> 17:47.798
Now, look who's walk,
walk, walking with purpose

17:47.800 --> 17:50.000
