17:57.343 --> 17:59.043
We're a notorious gangster couple now

17:59.045 --> 18:00.377
down at the Cineplex.

18:00.379 --> 18:03.214
That's right,
Han-nie and Clyde,

18:03.216 --> 18:04.748
but you know what, I'm fine.

18:04.750 --> 18:07.017
