18:08.421 --> 18:11.689
An obstructed view of my sweet, sweet ass?

18:11.691 --> 18:13.757
No, the satisfaction of knowing

18:13.759 --> 18:15.559
that you are just as selfish as me.

18:16.061 --> 18:17.695
What a selfish thing to say.

18:18.297 --> 18:21.392
You can walk, walk, walk away from me, Max,

18:21.393 --> 18:22.833
but you can't walk away from knowing

18:22.835 --> 18:24.101
that you split the scene.

18:24.103 --> 18:26.370
What? I thought you
were behind me,

18:26.372 --> 18:28.239
and besides, we couldn't both get caught.

18:28.241 --> 18:29.607
Who would live to tell the tale

18:29.609 --> 18:31.275
of the great Caroline Channing, the girl

18:31.277 --> 18:32.910
who couldn't walk fast enough?

18:32.912 --> 18:36.013
No, no, no, no, no.
Don't turn this around.

18:36.015 --> 18:38.449
Now, I see it, the whole "Max" of it all.

18:38.451 --> 18:40.184
When we got caught, you only thought

18:40.186 --> 18:41.785
about saving yourself,

18:41.787 --> 18:43.687
and you weren't defending poor Hallelujah.

18:43.689 --> 18:45.890
You just wanted fresh popcorn for yourself.

18:45.892 --> 18:48.025
What can I say?
I guess you're on to me.

18:48.527 --> 18:50.427
You said you'd take a bullet for me.

18:50.429 --> 18:52.029
You'd never take a bullet for me.

18:52.031 --> 18:54.565
Probably not.
No one ever takes a bullet.

18:54.567 --> 18:56.687
It's just something people say
that they don't mean,

18:56.688 --> 18:57.688
like, "how was your day?"

18:57.689 --> 19:00.504
Or, "we'll stop
if it hurts."

19:05.043 --> 19:07.411
Wow, so this is who we are,

19:07.413 --> 19:09.440
Two selfish girls who always put ourselves

19:09.441 --> 19:10.881
before everyone else and are willing

19:10.883 --> 19:12.216
to do anything to survive?

19:12.718 --> 19:14.285
Guess we are.

19:14.287 --> 19:16.620
Man, we're gonna crush
the cupcake competition.

19:17.122 --> 19:19.137
But, Max, even though we're ruthless,

19:19.138 --> 19:20.658
every now and then, on our own behalf,

19:20.660 --> 19:22.326
we do put ourselves second,

19:22.328 --> 19:24.962
and I guess that's
what makes us best friends.

19:25.714 --> 19:27.264
I don't think I've ever done that.

19:27.266 --> 19:28.465
Yes, you have.

19:28.467 --> 19:29.633
You let me stay on your couch

19:29.635 --> 19:31.468
