19:31.470 --> 19:33.170
I guess I did.

19:33.172 --> 19:36.907
And I gave you...

19:36.909 --> 19:38.611
Go ahead.

19:40.613 --> 19:43.133
Well, there must be something
where I didn't put myself first.

19:43.134 --> 19:45.316
Let me know when you find it.

19:48.520 --> 19:50.754
Sophie, just look at you.

19:50.756 --> 19:52.957
You couldn't look more scrumptious.

19:52.959 --> 19:55.092
Maybe I could

19:55.094 --> 20:00.364
with a little chocolate drizzled on me.

20:01.116 --> 20:03.601
Good, there you are, Han.

20:03.603 --> 20:07.504
I just have one question
that I have to ask you.

20:07.506 --> 20:09.807
What is your favorite musical?

20:09.809 --> 20:12.343
Is it <i>The Wiz?</i>

20:13.846 --> 20:16.180
Whiz, Max!
I found another one, right?

20:17.883 --> 20:19.450
How do you even know about this?

20:19.452 --> 20:23.721
Oleg told me
while we were having phone sex.

20:23.723 --> 20:26.457
And by phone sex, she means
we were using the phone

20:26.459 --> 20:27.993
in the sex.

20:29.895 --> 20:31.528
Don't worry, Han.

20:31.530 --> 20:34.331
A lot of older men
can't control their bladder.

20:34.333 --> 20:36.867
I am twenty-freaking-nine!

20:36.869 --> 20:39.703
What?

20:44.010 --> 20:46.010
I'm humiliated, Max.

20:46.012 --> 20:48.312
Hey, listen to me.

20:48.314 --> 20:49.580
You didn't sell Caroline out.

20:49.582 --> 20:51.048
A lot of people would have,

20:51.050 --> 20:52.816
but you just stood there like a man

20:52.818 --> 20:54.318
and peed your pants.

20:54.320 --> 20:56.720
That's true.
I did.

20:56.722 --> 20:58.029
By the way, Han, why were you

20:58.030 --> 20:59.590
