20:59.892 --> 21:01.091
Sometimes people bug me,

21:01.093 --> 21:02.528
and I need some time away.

21:04.030 --> 21:05.929
You know what, Han?

21:05.931 --> 21:07.097
You're cool.

21:07.099 --> 21:08.399
We're gonna hang sometime.

21:08.401 --> 21:09.400
Not now, not in a week,

